Hidden Markov Model Library
===========================


Overview
--------

An implementation of HMM with unlimited graph topology.
Categorial and Normal n-dimensional emssion distributions
are supported (with diagonal covariance matrix for the
Gaussian observations).


Algorithms implemented
----------------------

* Forward algorithm
* Viterbi algorithm
* Baum--Welch algorithm for training


